<subSubSection pageId="12" pageNumber="81" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="12.[151,1437,653,822]" pageId="12" pageNumber="81">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,314,761,786]" pageId="12" pageNumber="81">Diagnosis</emphasis>
. Genital field with one small platelet with 2–3 acetabula, located anteriorly to posterior two plates. The latter consisting of one plate with 7–9 acetabula and one with 20 acetabula. P4 with small setal tubercles.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
